HEADWORD: Rhinolophid
<hw>Rhi*nol"o*phid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Rhino-</ets> + Gr. <?/<?/<?/ crest.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
